{
  "texts": [
    "The best results are in bold.",
    "EA, IA, EO, and IO denote explicit aspect, implicit aspect, explicit opinion, and implicit opinion, respectively based on their syntactic relations in the review sentence and assigning sentiments (positive, negative, or neutral) using a sentiment lexicon.",
    "The second step is to identify the aspect category for each extracted triple.",
    "If the aspect is present in the training set, the most co-occurred aspect category is assigned as the final aspect category.",
    "Otherwise, the aspect category of the nearest aspect in the input review is adopted as the final aspect category."
  ]
}